(5) I missed all college essay deadlines because I was terrified of making any kind of decision and didn't know the first thing about colleges to begin with. So I went to community College at the urging of my then bf. And dropped out. Started using alcohol and drugs impulsively.

(4) had no real understanding of what that could mean. I had no real concept of what ADD/ADHD was other than "it's hard to pay attention." I knew nothing of my mood disorder or what could happen if I was off my meds. I fucked up so much of what I had going for me.
